<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.slate.com/id/2276919/">The NASA study of arsenic-based life was fatally flawed, say scientists. – Slate Magazine</a></span></li>
